==Behind the scenes==
Because Roan, Marasiah, and Mohrgan Fel are [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force users]], it is widely believed by fans that they are descendants of Jaina Solo, Jagged Fel's longtime love interest. This speculation was reinforced by the couple's marriage in ''[[Fate of the Jedi: Apocalypse]]''<ref name="Apocalypse" /> and the statement by [[Ania Solo]],<ref name="Legacy 16">[[Legacy (2013) 16|''Legacy'' (2013) 16]]</ref> a descendant of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]],<ref name="Legacy 5">[[Legacy (2013) 5|''Legacy'' (2013) 5]]</ref> that she was apparently a distant cousin of Marasiah Fel in [[Legacy (2013) 16|''Legacy'' (2013) 16]].<ref name="Legacy 16" />

